---
import Layout from './../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Spectrum">
  <main class="grow h-full text-color">
    <div
      class="h-96 p-4 flex flex-col items-start justify-center bg-gradient gap-4 mobile:h-80vh relative">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-full w-ful" id="particles-js"></div>
      <div class="w-full max-w-desktop mr-auto ml-auto relative z-10">
        <h1
          class="text-2xl mb-5 font-extrabold font-montserrat tracking-wider mobile:text-3xl mobile:max-w-96 md:text-5xl md:mb-10 md:max-w-xl lg:text-6xl lg:max-w-3xl">
          Spectrum
        </h1>
        <p class="max-w-60 md:max-w-md leading-6">
          At Spectrum, we are dedicated to helping bussisnes secure their digital environments through comprehensive 
          analysis and actionable insights. We conduct through assesments of your web pressence and virtual infrastructure,
          identifying vulnerabilities and offering targeted recommendations to enhace your cybersecurity posture. Our mission
          extends beyond protecion; we empower our clients with the knowledge and tools they need to build a resillient digital ecosystem.          
        </p>
           <p class="max-w-60 md:max-w-md leading-6">
          With <b>spectrum</b> your <b>security</b> is streamlined, proactive, and above all, effective.
           </p>
        
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
<script
  src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/particles.js@2.0.0/particles.min.js"
  is:inline></script>
<script src="./../app.js"></script>
